          Book Free Assessment
        </a>
        <a href="tel:437-545-0067" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-amber-500 px-8 py-4 font-bold text-navy-900 transition-all hover:bg-amber-400">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M2 3a1 1 0 011-1h2.153a1 1 0 01.986.836l.74 4.435a1 1 0 01-.54 1.06l-1.548.773a11.037 11.037 0 006.105 6.105l.774-1.548a1 1 0 011.059-.54l4.435.74a1 1 0 01.836.986V17a1 1 0 01-1 1h-2C7.82 18 2 12.18 2 5V3z" /></svg>
          437-545-0067
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center mt-8 text-sm">
        <a href="/services/legal-basement-conversion" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors">Requirements Guide</a>
        <span class="text-slate-600">|</span>
        <a href="/government-rebates" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors">All Rebates</a>
        <span class="text-slate-600">|</span>
        <a href="/services/underpinning" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors">Underpinning</a>
        <span class="text-slate-600">|</span>
        <a href="/second-unit" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors">All Cities</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
